4/17(Sat.)AI vs. Human Composer(Host:Pinn)<br /><br />AI vs. Human Composer<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/BJ1uXbRR2AQ">https://youtu.be/BJ1uXbRR2AQ</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Bach vs. AI: spot the difference<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/lv9W7qrYhbk">https://youtu.be/lv9W7qrYhbk</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Q1<br />1. Do you like music? Which kind of ?<br />2. Do you like Bach? Which kind of music is your favorite?<br />3. Have you listened to AI music? How do you think about AI and music?<br />Q2<br />1. How do you think about AI music?<br />2. Can music composers compete with AI?<br />3. Will  you create music with AI robot ?<br /><br />///////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri Apr 16, 2021 10:59 am</p><hr />
